BioTwin: AI-Powered Digital Health Twin for Predictive Healthcare

Submitted by: [Your Name]
Institute: IIT Roorkee
Department: Biosciences & Bioengineering

Vision

BioTwin aims to develop an AI-driven Digital Health Twin that creates a dynamic virtual representation of an individual’s health. It integrates lifestyle data, clinical reports, and biomarker information to enable early prediction of diseases and personalized preventive healthcare.

The objective is to shift healthcare from a reactive model to a predictive and preventive intelligence system.
